ts into the scale and mechanics of the ecological threat that is sound pollution in the ocean.<p><p>The lecture-performance was commissioned by TBA21–Academy</p>	Courtesy of Francesca Thyssen-Bornemisza and TBA21–Academy	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Other	\N	1	1	1	http://soundstoomany.com/	\N	CC BY-NC	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	f	f	\N
