te","Francesca Thyssen-Bornemisza","Eduardo Navarro","Ingo Niermann","Markus Reymann","Albert Serra","Teresa Solar"}	\N	\N	\N	Expedition	\N	1	1	1	https://ocean-archive.org/collection/30	\N	CC BY-NC	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	f	f	\N
