or future modelling exercises to improve spatial resolution, and integrate new variables (benefiting of local knowledge, inter alia) and scale-up so as to better deal with complex systems.</p>	\N	0	1	1	\N	\N	EN	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	{UNESCO-IOC}	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Courtesy of Consiglio Nazionale delle Ricerche	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	The UN Decade of Ocean Science for Sustainable Development 2021-2030: Mediterranean Workshop ‘The Mediterranean Sea We Need for the Future We Want’	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	https://ocean-archive.org/collection/21	\N	\N	t	\N
