-floor and threatening the stability of anthropogenic structures.</p>	\N	0	0	1	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Courtesy of the author(s)	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Nature: Scientific Reports	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-019-43027-7	\N	\N	t	\N
