apes were produced by Ears Up Sound Design and the lecture-performance was commissioned by TBA21–Academy.	\N	1	0	1	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	{"Francesca Thyssen-Bornemisza"}	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	Courtesy of Francesca Thyssen-Bornemisza and TBA21–Academy	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	https://ocean-archive.org/collection/31	\N	\N	t	\N
