bition 'Matter Fictions,' curated by Margarida Mendes, May 4 – August 30, 2016.	\N	1	0	1	\N	\N	EN	\N	\N	\N	Berardo Museum Collection, Lisbon	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Courtesy of Inhabitants	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	https://inhabitants-tv.org/may2016_miningforringwoodite.html	\N	\N	t	\N
