an (17.4°S to 61.0°N; 85.0 to 180.0°W) since 1999, we estimated a minimum of 21 290 t of floating microplastic.	\N	0	0	1	\N	\N	EN	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	\N	\N	\N	{"Kara Lavender Law","Skye Morét","Deborah S. Goodwin","Erik R. Zettler","Emelia DeForce","Tobias Kukulka","Giora Proskurowski"}	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/es4053076	\N	\N	t	\N
