e for ocean science and management; and enhancing capacity development, shared knowledge and technologies; Promote the concept of data sharing, education for sustainable development and active involvement of civil society and blue economy; Promote and implement regional cooperation, common laboratory facilities and centres in the Mediterranean Region; Integrate coastal and deep sea research promoting regional marine spatial planning in the region, and-upscaling clean Ocean regional initiatives and; Acknowledge the IMAP adopted in the framework of MAP BC as the minimum common base for monitoring and assessment of marine and coastal environment in the Med.</p>	\N	0	1	1	\N	\N	EN	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	{UNESCO-IOC}	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Courtesy of Consiglio Nazionale delle Ricerche	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	The UN Decade of Ocean Science for Sustainable Development 2021-2030: Mediterranean Workshop ‘The Mediterranean Sea We Need for the Future We Want’	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N
