 of how ocean waves are modeled and known in the northern and southern hemispheres. It concludes with a discussion of wave science as a kind of anthropology by other means.	\N	0	0	1	\N	\N	EN	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Courtesy of Stefan Helmreich	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Lewis Henry Morgan Lectures	\N	\N	\N	University of Rochester, Department of Anthropology	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	https://vimeo.com/114869573	\N	\N	t	\N
